content.html: December 1994, NYE "Hello, is Martin there?" "I'm afraid not. Can I help?" "Oh,ok. Could you tell me when the next train to London is?" "I think you've got the wrong number, we're 63947, the station is 63948." "But I've always called this number. And spoken to a Martin." 10/12

December 1994, NYE
"Hello, is Martin there?"
"I'm afraid not. Can I help?"
"Oh,ok. Could you tell me when the next train to London is?"
"I think you've got the wrong number, we're 63947, the station is 63948."
"But I've always called this number. And spoken to a Martin."
10/12
